<div class="nbunit" id="5Oct1930"><font color="red">5 October 1930</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Mrs Herbert Gorman): [My wife&apos;s] idea now is to have a summer residence in London so as to avoid the hundreds of pounds I spend yearly in hotel bills there </div>
